01:11:51.560 --> 01:11:52.560
than my wife."

01:11:52.560 --> 01:11:53.560
And it's so spontaneous, I mean, I don't have
to think, I know for definite that you are

01:11:53.560 --> 01:11:54.560
moving in the wrong direction or in the right
direction.

01:11:54.560 --> 01:11:55.560
Even the material movement are (inaudible).

01:11:55.560 --> 01:11:56.560
All of them have it, even they're great drivers
