01:11:56.560 --> 01:11:57.560
And immediately I know that you are going
on the wrong direction because the magnet

01:11:57.560 --> 01:11:58.560
immediately turns round.

01:11:58.560 --> 01:11:59.560
So the magnet is placed within you there but
it is to be awakened.

01:11:59.560 --> 01:12:00.560
