awakened - you become the truth, like the

01:12:00.560 --> 01:12:01.560
light that comes within, you start seeing
everything as far as your feelings are concerned,

01:12:01.560 --> 01:12:02.560
your experiencing is concerned.

01:12:02.560 --> 01:12:03.560
So you become the truth.

01:12:03.560 --> 01:12:04.560
Now one may say how truth could be love.

01:12:04.560 --> 01:12:05.560
That's a very common question.

01:12:05.560 --> 01:12:06.560
Truth cannot be love because, I mean, if you
tell somebody something that is truth, he

01:12:06.560 --> 01:12:07.560
may not like, and he may be unhappy and it
may not be dear to him, and he might be very,

01:12:07.560 --> 01:12:08.560
very worried about it.

01:12:08.560 --> 01:12:09.560
Manu said long time back that you should speak
the truth and you must speak the things which

01:12:09.560 --> 01:12:10.560
are dear to others.

01:12:10.560 --> 01:12:11.560
"Satyam vade, priyam vade."

01:12:11.560 --> 01:12:12.560
People said it's not possible, it's an absurd
situation, how can you do it?

01:12:12.560 --> 01:12:13.560
So Krishna has put something in between, he
said, "Satyam vade, hitam vade, priyam vade."

01:12:13.560 --> 01:12:14.560
You say something that is the truth, always
say the truth, and, saying something, hitam

01:12:14.560 --> 01:12:15.560
means for the pleasing of the spirit.

01:12:15.560 --> 01:12:16.560
That's the condition.

01:12:16.560 --> 01:12:17.560
And ultimately that becomes a very dear thing.

01:12:17.560 --> 01:12:18.560
In the beginning one may not like it, but
ultimately, this will be very much liked,

01:12:18.560 --> 01:12:19.560
this truth.

01:12:19.560 --> 01:12:20.560
So all these things he has put together and
said that, "You have to speak the truth, the

01:12:20.560 --> 01:12:21.560
truth has to be pleasing to the spirit, and
ultimately, the person is going to enjoy it."

01:12:21.560 --> 01:12:22.560
So the truth is everything is illusion, except
for the Divine of God that is all-pervading

01:12:22.560 --> 01:12:23.560
which you can feel through your spirit.

01:12:23.560 --> 01:12:24.560
This power has got telecommunications.

01:12:24.560 --> 01:12:25.560
It has got all that you have created in the
science.

01:12:25.560 --> 01:12:26.560
It can coordinate and cooperate.

01:12:26.560 --> 01:12:27.560
It has got all the angels and all the great
hosts to help it and to look after you.

01:12:27.560 --> 01:12:28.560
And the top, toppng the whole thing is the
quality that is love, is love.

01:12:28.560 --> 01:12:29.560
So it doesn't come to you like a sword, it
gives you the time to improve, to judge yourself,

01:12:29.560 --> 01:12:30.560
to rise, to grow.

01:12:30.560 --> 01:12:31.560
Just as a mother would look after her child,
forgive mistakes, see that the child rises

01:12:31.560 --> 01:12:32.560
and grows into complete manhood.

01:12:32.560 --> 01:12:33.560
So it is love and the love that is so powerful
is the truth; and it never fails, it never

01:12:33.560 --> 01:12:34.560
fails.

01:12:34.560 --> 01:12:35.560
For example you might think now a man like
Sadat has died.

01:12:35.560 --> 01:12:36.560
"Mother how do you explain?"

01:12:36.560 --> 01:12:37.560
I mean, you never die, that's one thing you
do not know.

01:12:37.560 --> 01:12:38.560
He can be born again, he would be born in
such a condition where he'll be much more

01:12:38.560 --> 01:12:39.560
effective.

01:12:39.560 --> 01:12:40.560
He has himself died at the top of his glory.

01:12:40.560 --> 01:12:41.560
I mean, for him, he's a (inaudible).

01:12:41.560 --> 01:12:42.560
If you see from his angle, everywhere in the
whole world, Sadat.

01:12:42.560 --> 01:12:43.560
Sa-dat, it's a big name too.

01:12:43.560 --> 01:12:44.560
But supposing he had fallen in his glory and
all that, then he would have died, then God

01:12:44.560 --> 01:12:45.560
would not have been just to him, I would say.

01:12:45.560 --> 01:12:46.560
But he died in all his glory and he can be
born again.

01:12:46.560 --> 01:12:47.560
And he can take a position from where he can
do much better work, in the name of God, in

01:12:47.560 --> 01:12:48.560
the field of God because now we don't have
to do any more work, otherwise in any other

01:12:48.560 --> 01:12:49.560
field.

01:12:49.560 --> 01:12:50.560
We have had enough of trains, we don't want
any more now.

01:12:50.560 --> 01:12:51.560
We have had enough of plastics, now we have
mountains.

01:12:51.560 --> 01:12:52.560
We've got too much of butter around, too much
of food, everything abit too much, I mean

01:12:52.560 --> 01:12:53.560
the house becomes a junk.

01:12:53.560 --> 01:12:54.560
In any field we have overdone things.

01:12:54.560 --> 01:12:55.560
We have exhausted this Mother Earth.

01:12:55.560 --> 01:12:56.560
Now what do we have to do.

01:12:56.560 --> 01:12:57.560
Only in one field and the field that is of
God's work you have to do.

01:12:57.560 --> 01:12:58.560
But first you have to get connected and then
do the God's work.

01:12:58.560 --> 01:12:59.560
And that connection is only through your spirit,
when you become absolute and you have the

01:12:59.560 --> 01:13:00.560
truth within you as a built-in awareness.

01:13:00.560 --> 01:13:01.560
It's the awareness that becomes the truth.

01:13:01.560 --> 01:13:02.560
So the first quality of the spirit is that
you become the truth, that you know the truth,

01:13:02.560 --> 01:13:03.560
that you take a stand on the truth.

01:13:03.560 --> 01:13:04.560
Look at Christ.

01:13:04.560 --> 01:13:05.560
He had nothing to do with women like Mary
Magdalene, I mean, nothing to do, I mean,

01:13:05.560 --> 01:13:06.560
he was virtue, he was innocence.

01:13:06.560 --> 01:13:07.560
But when he saw people were stoning her, he
took up a stand.

01:13:07.560 --> 01:13:08.560
He took up a stand.

01:13:08.560 --> 01:13:09.560
You have to take up a stand, stand on the
truth.

01:13:09.560 --> 01:13:10.560
And he said those who have not committed any
sin can throw, and you can throw the stone

01:13:10.560 --> 01:13:11.560
at me.

01:13:11.560 --> 01:13:12.560
And nobody did.

01:13:12.560 --> 01:13:13.560
He did this because he was standing on the
truth.

01:13:13.560 --> 01:13:14.560
He took a whip and whipped those people who
were selling in the temple of God.

01:13:14.560 --> 01:13:15.560
At eight, when he was a little boy, he went
and argued with learned people.

01:13:15.560 --> 01:13:16.560
Such people have no fear of anything.

01:13:16.560 --> 01:13:17.560
What is there to fear?

01:13:17.560 --> 01:13:18.560
When you are standing on the truth, what is
there to fear?

01:13:18.560 --> 01:13:19.560
Truth is such a light that it gives you complete
picture of the whole thing.

01:13:19.560 --> 01:13:20.560
There's nothing to fear.

01:13:20.560 --> 01:13:21.560
Your Father, He is compassion, He's ocean
of compassion.

01:13:21.560 --> 01:13:22.560
And He's ocean of love and ocean of forgiveness.

01:13:22.560 --> 01:13:23.560
And He is now within you.

01:13:23.560 --> 01:13:24.560
Who is more powerful than Him?

01:13:24.560 --> 01:13:25.560
It's very easy for many human beings to say,
"Oh, we don't believe in God."

01:13:25.560 --> 01:13:26.560
You believe it or not, He's there.

01:13:26.560 --> 01:13:27.560
Those who say, "We don't believe", it is better
that they should come and get their realisation

01:13:27.560 --> 01:13:28.560
and understand that there's very little time
left for such kind of nonsensical statements.

01:13:28.560 --> 01:13:29.560
I mean you can at the most say that I've not
felt God so far and I'm open, if I feel.

01:13:29.560 --> 01:13:30.560
But on what basis do you deny, what basis
have you got to say that you don't believe

01:13:30.560 --> 01:13:31.560
in God?

01:13:31.560 --> 01:13:32.560
Not only after realisation you can prove God,
but you can show His miracles.

01:13:32.560 --> 01:13:33.560
The second thing, the nature of spirit is
that he's chitta, he's the attention.

01:13:33.560 --> 01:13:34.560
He's the attention means when you become spiritually
enlightened your attention becomes enlightened.

01:13:34.560 --> 01:13:35.560
Now enlightenment, what we understand of these
lights is that the lights are falling here,

01:13:35.560 --> 01:13:36.560
and we can see things, that's all.

01:13:36.560 --> 01:13:37.560
But this attention which is being enlightened,
acts, it works, it has got loops, it has got

01:13:37.560 --> 01:13:38.560
weapons, it works.

01:13:38.560 --> 01:13:39.560
You have to see for yourself how your attention
works.

01:13:39.560 --> 01:13:40.560
Today there was somebody who went and told
one of the Sahaja Yogis that, "I was sitting

01:13:40.560 --> 01:13:41.560
there and I was getting all negative thoughts
and feeling horrible in my hands and I don't

01:13:41.560 --> 01:13:42.560
know why it was happening in the program."

01:13:42.560 --> 01:13:43.560
First he said, "Here you have come to pay
attention to Mother and to Her work and pay

01:13:43.560 --> 01:13:44.560
attention to your spirit.

01:13:44.560 --> 01:13:45.560
But if you're paying attention to all the
people here, then you're going to suffer."

01:13:45.560 --> 01:13:46.560
It's a very simple thing, where is your attention?

01:13:46.560 --> 01:13:47.560
Ask this question.

01:13:47.560 --> 01:13:48.560
This is a very common question in an Indian
home, a mother will ask a child, "Where is

01:13:48.560 --> 01:13:49.560
your attention?"

01:13:49.560 --> 01:13:50.560
The basis of Indian life is chitta nirodh,
is to fix your attention in a proper way.

01:13:50.560 --> 01:13:51.560
Where is your attention?

01:13:51.560 --> 01:13:52.560
Is it on your spirit?

01:13:52.560 --> 01:13:53.560
Or is it on somebody else, like, "My brother
is sitting here, my mother is sitting there,

01:13:53.560 --> 01:13:54.560
oh, that woman is very bad, she's jealous
of me," all these nonsense.

01:13:54.560 --> 01:13:55.560
Where is your attention?

01:13:55.560 --> 01:13:56.560
When you get realised then you start seeing
through the window of the spirit, your position

01:13:56.560 --> 01:13:57.560
changes.

01:13:57.560 --> 01:13:58.560
As you're looking at Me now, then you come
back here and start looking at you different.

01:13:58.560 --> 01:13:59.560
Till you're realised you are sitting before
Me.

01:13:59.560 --> 01:14:00.560
But once you're realised you come here and
see others from there, that's your fort.

01:14:00.560 --> 01:14:01.560
Nobody can touch you there.

01:14:01.560 --> 01:14:02.560
From there you'll see others, your attention
is detached.

01:14:02.560 --> 01:14:03.560
So the attention becomes enlightened after
realisation.

01:14:03.560 --> 01:14:04.560
You pay attention to anything, it works.

01:14:04.560 --> 01:14:05.560
It does work, no doubt, it fact.

01:14:05.560 --> 01:14:06.560
Those who've got realisation should try, try
your attention, but attention has to be pure.

01:14:06.560 --> 01:14:07.560
You have to purify your attention, and the
best way to purify it is to keep your agnya

01:14:07.560 --> 01:14:08.560
chakra open.

01:14:08.560 --> 01:14:09.560
When this centre is open, which is the centre
of Christ, which I've shown that it can only

01:14:09.560 --> 01:14:10.560
open through the Lord's Prayer, after realisation.

01:14:10.560 --> 01:14:11.560
When you open that, then you are in that state
where your attention is divine.

01:14:11.560 --> 01:14:12.560
And you'll be amazed how things work out,
even the smallest things, the material things,

01:14:12.560 --> 01:14:13.560
the useless things and the great things, and
the subtle and subtlest, and how you start

01:14:13.560 --> 01:14:14.560
growing.

01:14:14.560 --> 01:14:15.560
So the growth is to be achieved by purifying
your attention, and to purify this attention

01:14:15.560 --> 01:14:16.560
is to keep your agnya chakra open and be in
thoughtless awareness.

01:14:16.560 --> 01:14:17.560
You watch something, you don't think about
it.

01:14:17.560 --> 01:14:18.560
Zen said the same thing but I think people
didn't understand, you see, before realisation

01:14:18.560 --> 01:14:19.560
it's like telling about colours to a blind
man.

01:14:19.560 --> 01:14:20.560
Zen said the same thing, you watch the thing
without thinking about it.

01:14:20.560 --> 01:14:21.560
They created patterns which didn't mean anything,
which you see it without thinking.

01:14:21.560 --> 01:14:22.560
But that's only possible after realisation.

01:14:22.560 --> 01:14:23.560
So the thinking process minimises and you
start witnessing.

01:14:23.560 --> 01:14:24.560
The higher state than that of attention is
that you jump into Nirvikalpa Samadhi, into

01:14:24.560 --> 01:14:25.560
the state of doubtless awareness.

01:14:25.560 --> 01:14:26.560
Now it is not doubtlessness because you've
argued it out or anything.

01:14:26.560 --> 01:14:27.560
But it's a state where you're doubtless about
things.

01:14:27.560 --> 01:14:28.560
I mean the way you feel, the way you behave,
the way your attention is, you can make it

01:14:28.560 --> 01:14:29.560
out that "I'm doubtlessly there."

01:14:29.560 --> 01:14:30.560
The discrimination becomes so sharp that you
can just say, "This is so and so and so,"

01:14:30.560 --> 01:14:31.560
there's no fanaticism about it.

01:14:31.560 --> 01:14:32.560
As I told you this morning that if a blind
man cross over something and says, "Oh there's

01:14:32.560 --> 01:14:33.560
a snake here," and you believe it's a snake,
you believe that's a snake, that's fanaticism.

01:14:33.560 --> 01:14:34.560
Because he has no eyes to see and you believe
it's a snake, he says, "Oh, there is a snake

01:14:34.560 --> 01:14:35.560
there, I believe."

01:14:35.560 --> 01:14:36.560
But to a person who has eyes, he knows it's
a rope, it's just a rope.

01:14:36.560 --> 01:14:37.560
And he says, "No, it's not, it's a rope."

01:14:37.560 --> 01:14:38.560
But he has eyes and when he says with his
eyes, he can see that, that it's a rope, he

01:14:38.560 --> 01:14:39.560
means it, the truth, then he's not a fanatic.

01:14:39.560 --> 01:14:40.560
But he's standing on the truth.

01:14:40.560 --> 01:14:41.560
This subtle difference people don't understand.

01:14:41.560 --> 01:14:42.560
Fanaticism comes through blindness and the
truth comes through realisation.

01:14:42.560 --> 01:14:43.560
And at any cost you'll not give up the truth,
any cost.

01:14:43.560 --> 01:14:44.560
Now when I started My work in 1970, somehow
I knew all about these fake gurus and fake

01:14:44.560 --> 01:14:45.560
people, I knew about them.

01:14:45.560 --> 01:14:46.560
And in My first lecture, we had about, must
be having about two, three thousand people,

01:14:46.560 --> 01:14:47.560
very huge hall, and I told the names of all
these fake people and who they were in previous

01:14:47.560 --> 01:14:48.560
lives and what they did, by name.

01:14:48.560 --> 01:14:49.560
And everybody was amazed at Me, they were
frightened.

01:14:49.560 --> 01:14:50.560
There was a Maharajah who was a friend of
My husband and all that, and he came and told

01:14:50.560 --> 01:14:51.560
Me that, "Oh Mataji, I am very frightened
for you."

01:14:51.560 --> 01:14:52.560
I said, "Why?"

01:14:52.560 --> 01:14:53.560
He said, "These people are horrid, they mint
money, they mint their whole earnings out

01:14:53.560 --> 01:14:54.560
of it.

01:14:54.560 --> 01:14:55.560
How did you say these things openly, (inaudible),
they will shoot you."

01:14:55.560 --> 01:14:56.560
I said, "Let them shoot.

01:14:56.560 --> 01:14:57.560
I'll see who shoots Me."

01:14:57.560 --> 01:14:58.560
They said, "You see they will prosecute you."

01:14:58.560 --> 01:14:59.560
I said, "Let them prosecute."

01:14:59.560 --> 01:15:00.560
So many years have passed, nobody has dared
to say that I'm telling the lie.

01:15:00.560 --> 01:15:01.560
There is no fear.

01:15:01.560 --> 01:15:02.560
You love, but you don't love satanic people,
you don't love Satans.

01:15:02.560 --> 01:15:03.560
The Satan who has spoiled the Kundalini of
people, who have spoiled all the chances of

01:15:03.560 --> 01:15:04.560
their getting realisation, as a mother, do
you think I should say they're very good people?

01:15:04.560 --> 01:15:05.560
I'm not a political figure and I'm not seeking
election.

01:15:05.560 --> 01:15:06.560
Cannot be a compromise.

01:15:06.560 --> 01:15:07.560
That's what happens to you also.

01:15:07.560 --> 01:15:08.560
But by your own self-esteem, by your own glory,
people see, "Here is a leader", and you become

01:15:08.560 --> 01:15:09.560
the leader of the people.

01:15:09.560 --> 01:15:10.560
You can, there is nothing to be frightened
of.

01:15:10.560 --> 01:15:11.560
There should be no half-bakes, as Christ,
as he read it out to you, that luke-warm people

01:15:11.560 --> 01:15:12.560
he spits them out of the mouth.

01:15:12.560 --> 01:15:13.560
If you're hot, if you're devils, he'll fight
you; if you're cold, you're my children.

01:15:13.560 --> 01:15:14.560
But luke-warm people are cunning, because
all kinds of forces are pulling, there's no

01:15:14.560 --> 01:15:15.560
progress of any kind.

01:15:15.560 --> 01:15:16.560
You come, you come, negative, positive, they're
pulled this way, that way.

01:15:16.560 --> 01:15:17.560
There cannot be compromise with truth.

01:15:17.560 --> 01:15:18.560
And then you would see you will have the real
connecting force, the real blessings of God,

01:15:18.560 --> 01:15:19.560
in every way.

01:15:19.560 --> 01:15:20.560
You don't have to worry about money, you don't
have to worry about anything, it all works

01:15:20.560 --> 01:15:21.560
out, everything works out.

01:15:21.560 --> 01:15:22.560
You can't believe it how much it works out.

