I'll tell you about these Australians: Australians
were finding it very difficult to get a place

01:15:23.560 --> 01:15:24.560
to have an ashram, and, one day, frantically
one of the girls telephoned to me, "Mother,

01:15:24.560 --> 01:15:25.560
we cannot have a place, now we don't know
where to go, we've sold our houses, we have

01:15:25.560 --> 01:15:26.560
no place to go to."

01:15:26.560 --> 01:15:27.560
I said, "Don't you worry, tomorrow, you'll
get it."

01:15:27.560 --> 01:15:28.560
And she was surprised how I told her, "Tomorrow
you'll get it."

01:15:28.560 --> 01:15:29.560
After telephoning and all that, she went home
and she received a call, I mean there was

01:15:29.560 --> 01:15:30.560
a call from a estate agent.

01:15:30.560 --> 01:15:31.560
When they went to see him next day he said,
"There is an ashram available, would you like

01:15:31.560 --> 01:15:32.560
to have it?".

01:15:32.560 --> 01:15:33.560
At a very cheap rate, they got a beautiful
house for the ashram.

01:15:33.560 --> 01:15:34.560
In London, we had some sort of a small ashram,
they were finding it very difficult for all

01:15:34.560 --> 01:15:35.560
these people to live there, because they wanted
to live together.

01:15:35.560 --> 01:15:36.560
They said, "Mother, we must have some more
room and some more place."

01:15:36.560 --> 01:15:37.560
I said, "Alright you just pray, it will work
out."

01:15:37.560 --> 01:15:38.560
You won't believe, we had started a co-op
in London, and they said it will take eight

01:15:38.560 --> 01:15:39.560
years to get a room out of this co-op.

01:15:39.560 --> 01:15:40.560
That's London for you, just the opposite of
America.

