generous, I mean, I try to give away so many
things but still My house, oh God!

01:16:05.560 --> 01:16:06.560
You can't imagine, you can't imagine, in their
wedding I gave fifty-one saris, fifty-one,

01:16:06.560 --> 01:16:07.560
thinking that now I'll some left from these
saris.

01:16:07.560 --> 01:16:08.560
Again I went back, they're still there.

