01:16:11.560 --> 01:16:12.560
Where are they lost, where are they?

01:16:12.560 --> 01:16:13.560
That's something still there, they are to
be saved, because as I told you Christ is

01:16:13.560 --> 01:16:14.560
going to come back with eleven destructive
powers and there's going to be no question,

01:16:14.560 --> 01:16:15.560
no realisation, just...

