That joy of oneness even in separation the
oneness I feel, it's such a joy..., that cannot

01:17:29.560 --> 01:17:30.560
be expressed in words, that silent (inaudible)
of your heart, that is also joy.

01:17:30.560 --> 01:17:31.560
Joy is absolute, it comes through seeing,
