01:17:43.560 --> 01:17:44.560
Your life is (inaudible) knowledge because
you're seeing the truth, the knowledge.

01:17:44.560 --> 01:17:45.560
That's the gift of the brain, is the central
path as I just said, the awareness.

01:17:45.560 --> 01:17:46.560
Then you feel your chitta, your attention
which is enlightened, and you're blasted with

01:17:46.560 --> 01:17:47.560
it.

01:17:47.560 --> 01:17:48.560
You see the miracles happening, that happening,
you're just blasted.

01:17:48.560 --> 01:17:49.560
Then the third thing happens; is the joy,
that you are in joy all the time.

01:17:49.560 --> 01:17:50.560
You cannot be serious for more than two minutes,
it's very difficult to keep serious.

01:17:50.560 --> 01:17:51.560
The sense of humour is so beautiful, you'll
never use vulgarity or hurting things or coarser

01:17:51.560 --> 01:17:52.560
remarks, but the whole thing is so beautiful.

01:17:52.560 --> 01:17:53.560
When you speak, people feel the flowers throwing
their fragrance at you.

01:17:53.560 --> 01:17:54.560
Every action that you do creates joy, ripple
of joy.

01:17:54.560 --> 01:17:55.560
Every movement you create, every rhythm you
speak it gives you joy.

01:17:55.560 --> 01:17:56.560
That time you feel perfected.

01:17:56.560 --> 01:17:57.560
When you see a picture which is beautiful,
immediately you go into thoughtless awareness,

01:17:57.560 --> 01:17:58.560
and the complete joy of that creation starts
blossoming, you just feel the joy.

01:17:58.560 --> 01:17:59.560
When you become silent, you don't think much,
you don't think, you become the joy, anand.

01:17:59.560 --> 01:18:00.560
That's the perfect state in which you feel
peace, it's so beautiful that you want to

01:18:00.560 --> 01:18:01.560
be there all the time.

01:18:01.560 --> 01:18:02.560
This joy is the movement of your ocean of
love.

01:18:02.560 --> 01:18:03.560
It's the beautiful movement of the clouds
that you see.

01:18:03.560 --> 01:18:04.560
It's fantastic, you just get drenched into
it and you do everything for love's sake and

01:18:04.560 --> 01:18:05.560
you don't think you're doing it for love's
sake, you do not see that way, you just do

01:18:05.560 --> 01:18:06.560
it, because it's so joy-giving; that it is
the greatest thing, you may have anything

01:18:06.560 --> 01:18:07.560
in the world will not be that much joy-giving
as this joy of the spirit within.

01:18:07.560 --> 01:18:08.560
You'll never feel lonely, you're never bored,
whether you're alone or with anyone, you are

01:18:08.560 --> 01:18:09.560
in joy.

