One should understand that if you get your
self-realisation or if somebody says that

01:18:10.560 --> 01:18:11.560
they're giving you some positive mind, you
should know, are you peaceful within you,

01:18:11.560 --> 01:18:12.560
are you joy; forget about the collective consciousness,
is your health alright?

01:18:12.560 --> 01:18:13.560
That's the minimum of minimum.

01:18:13.560 --> 01:18:14.560
The whole system changes.

01:18:14.560 --> 01:18:15.560
I just pray that all of you should achieve
that state of joy by the time I come here

01:18:15.560 --> 01:18:16.560
next year.

01:18:16.560 --> 01:18:17.560
And I hope you grow in it by taking up a stand
on the truth.

01:18:17.560 --> 01:18:18.560
Grow into it.

01:18:18.560 --> 01:18:19.560
You progress into it.

01:18:19.560 --> 01:18:20.560
It's so wonderful and so beautiful and that's
what your Father wants you to have.

01:18:20.560 --> 01:18:21.560
He's the most generous Father; He can't enjoy
His kingdom unless and until He has given

01:18:21.560 --> 01:18:22.560
it to you, that He has made you sit on His
throne.

01:18:22.560 --> 01:18:23.560
That's the greatest joy that He wants to have
and that's what you should achieve, that's

01:18:23.560 --> 01:18:24.560
what you should have, that's your right to
have.

01:18:24.560 --> 01:18:25.560
This is what is self-realisation - you become
just the master.

01:18:25.560 --> 01:18:26.560
You don't have to consult anyone, you know
it.

01:18:26.560 --> 01:18:27.560
You have to just consult your spirit, through
your vibratory awareness and you know it.

01:18:27.560 --> 01:18:28.560
These are the blessings of self-realisation,
into which you have to grow and as you grow

01:18:28.560 --> 01:18:29.560
you start manifesting your powers.

01:18:29.560 --> 01:18:30.560
You can raise the Kundalini, you can give
realisation at the very outset.

01:18:30.560 --> 01:18:31.560
Imagine the Kundalini moves under your fingers,
nobody can believe it but it has happened

01:18:31.560 --> 01:18:32.560
now.

01:18:32.560 --> 01:18:33.560
Even very, very great saints, you see, there
is a very great saint who is more than hundred

01:18:33.560 --> 01:18:34.560
and eight years of age, and he asked Me, "Mother,
I have spent thousands of years to get these

01:18:34.560 --> 01:18:35.560
vibrations and these people have got it without
any (inaudible)."

01:18:35.560 --> 01:18:36.560
I said, "Why did you do it, who asked you
to do it?

01:18:36.560 --> 01:18:37.560
If you'd taken it easy, you'd have got it."

01:18:37.560 --> 01:18:38.560
He's a very sweet fellow, but because he's
got it through his efforts he has that feeling

01:18:38.560 --> 01:18:39.560
that, "I've got it through my efforts."

01:18:39.560 --> 01:18:40.560
You'll never get it through effort, I tell
you.

01:18:40.560 --> 01:18:41.560
When you're finished with your efforts you
just get it, maybe in an abstraction, or maybe...Yes,

01:18:41.560 --> 01:18:42.560
when Buddha was tired, finished, fagged-out,
then he got his realisation.

01:18:42.560 --> 01:18:43.560
When you stop your efforts then only you'll
get your realisation.

01:18:43.560 --> 01:18:44.560
So why to boast of your efforts, I told him.

01:18:44.560 --> 01:18:45.560
He's a very powerful man because he's done
lots of things and he always goes on a big,

01:18:45.560 --> 01:18:46.560
very big tiger and because he's hurt himself,
he says that people have beaten him, so he's

01:18:46.560 --> 01:18:47.560
hurt himself so he always uses a tiger.

01:18:47.560 --> 01:18:48.560
And he's a man with the idea that he has this
power, that power.

01:18:48.560 --> 01:18:49.560
When I went to see him, I knew that because
he told people that Mother has come, so you

01:18:49.560 --> 01:18:50.560
go and see Her and all that and I knew he
was there so I went to see him.

01:18:50.560 --> 01:18:51.560
When I went to see him, we had to climb about
three miles, one has to walk up, and I was

01:18:51.560 --> 01:18:52.560
walking up and when I reached there it was
raining and I got completely drenched.

01:18:52.560 --> 01:18:53.560
And this fellow is supposed powers over the
rain.

01:18:53.560 --> 01:18:54.560
And he was so angry when I went there he was
sitting on a little seat of his made of some

01:18:54.560 --> 01:18:55.560
straws.

01:18:55.560 --> 01:18:56.560
He was doing like this, like this, very angry.

01:18:56.560 --> 01:18:57.560
So I didn't say anything, I went inside his
thing and sat down there in that drenched

01:18:57.560 --> 01:18:58.560
condition.

01:18:58.560 --> 01:18:59.560
He came down and he said, "Mother, did you
do this to kill my ego?"

01:18:59.560 --> 01:19:00.560
I said, "What, I didn't do anything.

01:19:00.560 --> 01:19:01.560
What did I do?"

01:19:01.560 --> 01:19:02.560
He said, "This rain wouldn't listen to me."

01:19:02.560 --> 01:19:03.560
I said, "Now, don't be angry, sit down.

01:19:03.560 --> 01:19:04.560
Haven't you bought a sari for Me, and you
are a sanyasi, I won't take a sari from a

01:19:04.560 --> 01:19:05.560
sanyasi now.

01:19:05.560 --> 01:19:06.560
You've have got a sari for Me isn't it?

01:19:06.560 --> 01:19:07.560
So I have to get drenched, otherwise I will
not take a sari from you."

01:19:07.560 --> 01:19:08.560
And the whole temper melted, whole temper
melted away.

01:19:08.560 --> 01:19:09.560
Then I said, "It was necessary the water to
flow over My body so that all the plains around

01:19:09.560 --> 01:19:10.560
you become beautiful, is vibrated with water."

01:19:10.560 --> 01:19:11.560
