he doesn't talk to Me like ordinary human

01:19:11.560 --> 01:19:12.560
beings talk.

01:19:12.560 --> 01:19:13.560
His style is different because he recognises,
he knows who I am.

01:19:13.560 --> 01:19:14.560
He's a very different being, and a day will
